                  #stack
                    i Node.js, Express.js, Markdown
                  #desc
                    | A simple static blog engine. Built for extensibility and use of use.
                  a(href='https://github.com/wahidrahim/carpet', target='_blank')
                    | https://github.com/wahidrahim/carpet

                // MEAN-TODO-APP
                .item
                  img.img-responsive(src='http://i.imgur.com/uHPveze.jpg')
